                <i class="bi bi-envelope-paper-heart fs-1 mb-3 storinta-icon-accent"></i>
                <h2 class="storinta-section-title-light">Yeni Hikayelerden ve Özel İçeriklerden Haberdar Olun!</h2>
                <p class="lead text-light opacity-75 mb-4 px-lg-5">
